[SN]TITLE[SN]
Shimna Road: Bricks thrown at cars in Newcastle

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A motorist has been left badly shaken after a brick smashed her windscreen as she drove along a road in Newcastle, County Down.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
It happened on Shimna Road at about 20:15 GMT on Friday.
A second car travelling behind the woman's car, also sustained a dent.
Police have appealed for information about the incident.
